{"tid":648733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鹹田淪陷】人去樓空變垃圾崗 內地客反指摘衞生設施不足","createTime":"2018-05-01T03:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T07:50:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":169,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"4baa20d5e7bd1b2fe629777396a83471913ee414","tid":648733,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525141272_9d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525141272_9d89.jpg&h=dc46cd3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五一黄金周西貢鹹田灣大露營18小時，有內地客總結行程，認為缺德團友應深切反省，不過就有團友認為香港應增加衞生設施，給訪客方便。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午3時才到鹹田灣紥營的內地團，短暫享受沙幼水清的沙灘。有團友早起在沙灘緩步跑，有人則檢拾枯葉生火烘乾衣服。大部分團友早上7時便自發起來嗽口，收拾行裝營幕，交還出租的營帳予士多，繼續行程經西灣及東壩解散後便返回內地。有團友說，團隊主要活動是徒步，因此必須那麼早起。有露營團安排團友乘快艇離開。整塊鹹田灣沙灘暫時回復原貌與寧靜。<br />\n<br />\n記者晚夜夜探鹹田公廁，原先用作洗手的水盆塞滿相信是團友棄置的胸圍、波鞋、短褲、廚餘等雜物。團友陳小姐來港4次，最初都是購物吃喝，最近經朋友介紹參加露營行山團。她直指，有部分缺德團友不理別人感受，應好好加強保育意識，但就有跟隨上海學校親子團的家長建議香港政府應定期找人打掃公廁，增加衞生設施。<br />\n<br />\n有清潔承判商隨即清理營友違下的垃圾、燒烤灰燼、相信是團友摸來的海膽。承判清潔工人說，今年五一內地露營團不算多，最跨張有700營幕，幾乎填滿整個海灘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138112_4f19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138112_4f19.jpg&h=abd2b501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138113_dad8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138113_dad8.jpg&h=1849ae7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138944_39c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138944_39c7.jpg&h=68177bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525140994_da56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525140994_da56.jpg&h=bac8de94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525140996_13bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525140996_13bc.jpg&h=65699dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138114_bcea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138114_bcea.jpg&h=d4684ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58139128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58139128&d=uWXdQhWoVnubLJeAKiDwLgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fd25946f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58139128&h=4573932c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58139128</a>"},{"pid":"f9cc0ceb3248357ea723f828e184799c635a4426","tid":648733,"uid":112416,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"仆你個街"},{"pid":"29ff95f40bf1c0e0128081f0b7fcee3b0be3c847","tid":648733,"uid":52942,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"d牛居然唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好感動"},{"pid":"a967c804e28a51f67b563f2965de5040384c0a76","tid":648733,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"