br />\n返去同共產黨講啦，鄰國d公廁咪仲污糟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fef54b9d2441cc9e2a4e66c31e1db1260ece133","tid":648733,"uid":47819,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲個名真係改得無撚錯<br />\n<br />\n果度唔係發展畀你外國遊客玩樂嘅地方<br />\n無人關心你夠唔夠衛生設施用囉仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係唔撚想你地嚟呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"a7ae0139395e4a2d494f61312fc376d14cfe1506","tid":648733,"uid":47819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"全世界每個角落都要改到畀你蝗國人去玩嘅咩cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f40635f75f43ca3675f5fcfbd90ce4073434ec","tid":648733,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲所到之處，必家滿目瘡痍"},{"pid":"468d3ab6aae3fd674c4f453594c4fcbf11ae3df8","tid":648733,"uid":135767,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a5e6e61dba3017bba843cd2f7346e4060d8bb0d","tid":648733,"uid":11001,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://everydaylifeinmaoschina.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/e7be8ee59bbde697b6e4bba3e591a8e5888a1950e5b9b412e69c8811e697a5e79a84e5b081e99da2efbc8ce4babae789a9e698afe6af9be6b3bde4b89ce38082.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=9999\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feverydaylifeinmaoschina.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F02%2Fe7be8ee59bbde697b6e4bba3e591a8e5888a1950e5b9b412e69c8811e697a5e79a84e5b081e99da2efbc8ce4babae789a9e698afe6af9be6b3bde4b89ce38082.jpg%3Fw%3D1400%26h%3D9999&h=90481b1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c3ba8108f917151febbd3404ff67094e66bd177","tid":648733,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468d3ab6aae3fd674c4f453594c4fcbf1