pg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138113_dad8.jpg&h=1849ae7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138944_39c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138944_39c7.jpg&h=68177bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525140994_da56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525140994_da56.jpg&h=bac8de94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525140996_13bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525140996_13bc.jpg&h=65699dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180501/large/1525138114_bcea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F1525138114_bcea.jpg&h=d4684ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58139128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58139128&d=uWXdQhWoVnubLJeAKiDwLgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fd25946f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F58139128&h=4573932c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180501/58139128</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"留低個胸圍係咩玩法?許願啊？?"},{"pid":"1b6a69b531ea394d2e48204a97aabeccec2fcc73","tid":648733,"uid":10998,"like":1,"dislike":0,